---
---
<section class="section about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="fade-up">About Me</h2>
    <div class="about-content fade-up">
      <p class="text-lead">
        I am a passionate software developer focused on crafting clean, high-performance web experiences. With a strong foundation in modern Javascript frameworks and a keen eye for minimalist design, I bridge the gap between aesthetics and functionality.
      </p>
      <div class="about-details">
        <div>
          <h3>Experience</h3>
          <p>5+ Years building web products</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Focus</h3>
          <p>Frontend Architecture & Motion Design</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-content {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  
  .text-lead {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #e5e5e5;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .about-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #333;
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  .about-details h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-details p {
    color: #a3a3a3;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
</style>
